Interface LeaveBuilding

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface LeaveBuilding
This interface allows the person to request to leave the building.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    int generateLeaveAtTick()
    Generate leave at tick.
    void goToGround​(int currentTick)
    Lets the person request the ground floor when they want to leave the building.

  • Method Details

    • generateLeaveAtTick

      int generateLeaveAtTick()
      Generate leave at tick.
      Returns:
      int This is the tick that will be added onto the current tick, therefore determining when the person will request to leave.
